1
00:00:00,009 --> 00:02:00,009
( Watch on www.kissasia.co, .club, .be, .org, .net, .id, .xyz )

2
00:02:15,673 --> 00:02:18,259
Why is that girl here?

3
00:02:19,344 --> 00:02:20,387
President Ace.

4
00:02:20,512 --> 00:02:22,680
Fritzy is still the SSG Secretary.

5
00:02:22,908 --> 00:02:24,024
Get out of my sight,

6
00:02:24,484 --> 00:02:25,860
Ms. Fritzy Saldivar.

7
00:02:26,393 --> 00:02:27,393
Bitch.

8
00:02:29,210 --> 00:02:30,419
From now on.

9
00:02:30,444 --> 00:02:33,530
Ms. Zein Shion is
the new secretary of HU.

10
00:02:38,321 --> 00:02:39,321
Follow me.

11
00:02:44,911 --> 00:02:45,954
The Dark Hell Jail

12
00:02:46,538 --> 00:02:47,580
is waiting for you.

13
00:02:48,915 --> 00:02:50,291
If I were you, Zein.

14
00:02:50,588 --> 00:02:52,173
I'd step aside from your position.

15
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:56,673
You won't like it when
he shows his true colors.

16
00:02:57,048 --> 00:02:59,008
Where are your music sheets?

17
00:02:59,801 --> 00:03:01,344
It's okay ma'am. We can share.

18
00:03:02,554 --> 00:03:03,805
Thanks.

19
00:03:04,931 --> 00:03:06,641
You've been saving my
ass since earlier.

20
00:03:07,058 --> 00:03:08,058
I didn't catch your name.

21
00:03:09,185 --> 00:03:10,353
My name is Nazzer Lumia.

22
00:03:12,596 --> 00:03:14,473
You're the leader of
the Black Blood Gang?

23
00:03:24,278 --> 00:03:25,918
When the gangs have made you their target

24
00:03:28,652 --> 00:03:30,446
you will never know peace.

25
00:04:02,197 --> 00:04:03,823
Raven Robles,

26
00:04:05,105 --> 00:04:06,398
Paulo Roxas,

27
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:08,330
Jules Santos.

28
00:04:14,250 --> 00:04:16,627
It seems that the people here
have been disrespecting

29
00:04:16,628 --> 00:04:18,463
the authority of the
student council.

30
00:04:18,922 --> 00:04:19,922
Am I right?

31
00:04:20,738 --> 00:04:22,615
Be better at doing your jobs.

32
00:04:23,384 --> 00:04:26,763
The council cannot afford
to lose its power.

33
00:04:27,722 --> 00:04:28,890
Do you understand?

34
00:04:30,689 --> 00:04:31,731
Am I clear?

35
00:04:44,134 --> 00:04:45,177
I'm sorry.

36
00:04:45,586 --> 00:04:46,628
Ms. Shion.

37
00:04:47,742 --> 00:04:49,493
Do you want us
to move this meeting

38
00:04:49,494 --> 00:04:51,120
so you can get some snacks?

39
00:04:56,305 --> 00:04:57,389
Supremo

40
00:04:57,801 --> 00:04:59,594
with all due respect

41
00:04:59,954 --> 00:05:01,205
stop overreacting.

42
00:05:02,090 --> 00:05:05,176
You're not the only one
keen on stopping the killings.

43
00:05:05,869 --> 00:05:07,287
Don't be dramatic.

44
00:05:08,096 --> 00:05:10,014
I know she's hot-headed

45
00:05:10,515 --> 00:05:13,059
- but this disrespect is on another level.
- Ms. Shion.

46
00:05:13,977 --> 00:05:15,687
Let's just see what happens.

47
00:05:16,020 --> 00:05:17,729
Maybe you'll get
your position back.

48
00:05:17,730 --> 00:05:19,732
Can you repeat
what you just said?

49
00:05:23,342 --> 00:05:24,844
You heard me loud and clear.

50
00:05:29,826 --> 00:05:31,661
You still lack disclipine.

51
00:05:32,988 --> 00:05:33,988
Onel.

52
00:05:34,621 --> 00:05:35,456
Supremo.

53
00:05:35,481 --> 00:05:37,606
Get the files
Madam Violet asked for.

54
00:05:37,709 --> 00:05:39,210
Copy that, Supremo.

55
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:44,840
And now

56
00:05:46,092 --> 00:05:47,302
as your punishment

57
00:05:49,749 --> 00:05:51,167
when Onel gets back

58
00:05:52,765 --> 00:05:54,350
photocopy all of it.

59
00:05:54,475 --> 00:05:55,518
Bring it here

60
00:05:55,727 --> 00:05:57,353
then bring it to
the admin office.

61
00:05:58,062 --> 00:05:59,606
Copy that, Supremo.

62
00:06:02,507 --> 00:06:04,091
At least I'll be away
from all of you

63
00:06:04,232 --> 00:06:05,232
even for a moment.

64
00:06:05,257 --> 00:06:06,257
Supremo.

65
00:06:06,867 --> 00:06:09,160
Isn't Zein's
punishment too light

66
00:06:09,185 --> 00:06:11,020
for the insults she said to you?

67
00:06:12,702 --> 00:06:14,412
Are you questioning my methods?

68
00:06:14,621 --> 00:06:15,621
Fritzy

69
00:06:16,815 --> 00:06:17,858
besides

70
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,848
you don't have the right to
voice your opinion anymore

71
00:06:22,235 --> 00:06:24,070
since you're no longer
a part of the SSG.

72
00:06:26,883 --> 00:06:29,302
My apologies, Supremo.

73
00:06:30,678 --> 00:06:34,682
We need all the help
we can get from our members

74
00:06:36,392 --> 00:06:38,311
even if it's from that
disrespectful brat.

75
00:06:40,563 --> 00:06:41,564
Now

76
00:06:42,523 --> 00:06:44,192
what's the next agenda?

77
00:08:34,093 --> 00:08:37,054
You're lucky that this is
your punishment, Ms. Shion.

78
00:08:37,835 --> 00:08:41,381
Thought for sure he was going to
drag you to the Dark Hell Jail.

79
00:08:42,977 --> 00:08:44,896
Disappointed, Onel?

80
00:08:46,105 --> 00:08:48,107
I'm hurt you would
think that, Ms. Shion.

81
00:08:48,733 --> 00:08:50,359
But no, not disappointed

82
00:08:51,444 --> 00:08:52,612
surprised

83
00:08:53,362 --> 00:08:56,783
it seems like Supremo has
a soft spot for you.

84
00:08:58,617 --> 00:09:02,037
I don't need that or want his help.

85
00:09:03,648 --> 00:09:05,608
Maybe you’re right

86
00:09:06,523 --> 00:09:08,483
it pays to be cautious.

87
00:09:08,963 --> 00:09:11,174
It's dangerous to
get close with Supremo

88
00:09:15,551 --> 00:09:17,970
we don't know
what he's capable of.

89
00:09:19,854 --> 00:09:23,650
It’s like befriending a wild animal.

90
00:09:24,102 --> 00:09:25,770
You mean a snake.

91
00:09:27,722 --> 00:09:29,974
You're joking now, Ms. Shion

92
00:09:31,573 --> 00:09:34,659
if you thought that
the Dark Hell Jail

93
00:09:35,238 --> 00:09:39,242
was the worst punishment
Supremo can give

94
00:09:39,690 --> 00:09:41,775
you thought wrong.

95
00:09:44,137 --> 00:09:45,430
I'm ready whatever it is.

96
00:09:49,752 --> 00:09:51,003
Are you sure?

97
00:09:51,866 --> 00:09:55,995
Whatever nightmare you're
losing sleep over every night...

98
00:09:56,198 --> 00:10:00,327
like a predator
playing with its prey...

99
00:10:02,223 --> 00:10:03,641
Are you done now?

100
00:10:03,858 --> 00:10:06,652
Can't you just do
as you're told?

101
00:10:06,936 --> 00:10:08,938
I have work to do.

102
00:10:12,608 --> 00:10:17,613
I hope you finish your punishment
as soon as possible, Ms. Shion.

103
00:10:32,034 --> 00:10:33,202
Soft spot?

104
00:10:33,478 --> 00:10:37,398
From a person who
locks people up in the Dark Hell Jail?

105
00:10:38,191 --> 00:10:41,610
From a person who punished me

106
00:10:41,721 --> 00:10:44,640
just because I was
drinking water during a meeting?

107
00:10:45,182 --> 00:10:47,143
Is Vice Onel joking?

108
00:10:48,581 --> 00:10:49,581
Whatever.

109
00:10:50,487 --> 00:10:51,905
But this is for the best

110
00:10:52,148 --> 00:10:53,648
at least I'm away from them

111
00:10:53,649 --> 00:10:55,610
especially from Supremo.

112
00:10:57,862 --> 00:10:59,614
Whoever she is

113
00:10:59,739 --> 00:11:01,824
she's too audacious.

114
00:11:02,033 --> 00:11:03,158
Oh my gosh.

115
00:11:03,159 --> 00:11:05,035
She thinks she's all that.

116
00:11:05,036 --> 00:11:07,288
Oh, Zein is here.

117
00:11:12,752 --> 00:11:14,337
Well, well, well

118
00:11:14,503 --> 00:11:16,255
so the rumors are right.

119
00:11:16,464 --> 00:11:20,468
You're the new secretary of the
Supreme Student Government.

120
00:11:21,636 --> 00:11:24,764
Well, you must be quite proud.

121
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:28,476
But don't be too proud

122
00:11:28,726 --> 00:11:31,395
because you're still
their errand girl.

123
00:11:31,584 --> 00:11:32,876
Not like a queen

124
00:11:32,901 --> 00:11:35,195
but more like a slave.

125
00:11:35,774 --> 00:11:37,734
Low class.

126
00:11:42,657 --> 00:11:43,657
Move aside.

127
00:11:50,581 --> 00:11:51,832
I said move.

128
00:11:57,380 --> 00:11:58,923
Oh my god

129
00:11:59,083 --> 00:12:00,668
can you still stand?

130
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:03,004
How adorable.

131
00:12:03,219 --> 00:12:06,555
You're still unaware of your
place in this school?

132
00:12:08,724 --> 00:12:10,476
If I spit right now

133
00:12:11,060 --> 00:12:16,232
people here would see that my
saliva has more value than you.

134
00:12:16,899 --> 00:12:19,693
That's how far we are
from each other.

135
00:12:19,694 --> 00:12:21,112
So if I were you

136
00:12:21,487 --> 00:12:23,238
stop with that attitude.

137
00:12:23,239 --> 00:12:24,447
Because you

138
00:12:24,448 --> 00:12:26,367
will never be better than me.

139
00:12:26,492 --> 00:12:27,952
You never will be.

140
00:12:28,327 --> 00:12:30,913
You're like dirt on my shoes.

141
00:12:34,709 --> 00:12:37,377
I don't care about the
opinion of a girl

142
00:12:37,378 --> 00:12:39,088
who monitors her rank

143
00:12:39,964 --> 00:12:42,466
and is too conscious
of her image.

144
00:12:43,293 --> 00:12:45,003
You're just showing everyone

145
00:12:45,428 --> 00:12:47,722
your real face.

146
00:12:49,747 --> 00:12:51,540
An insecure little bitch.

147
00:12:52,987 --> 00:12:55,239
I'd laugh if it weren't so pathetic.

148
00:12:57,046 --> 00:12:58,544
H-how dare you!

149
00:12:59,274 --> 00:13:00,984
Do you know who I am?

150
00:13:03,411 --> 00:13:04,954
Your slap hurts.

151
00:13:05,781 --> 00:13:07,825
Fifty degrees if I'd rate it

152
00:13:08,576 --> 00:13:11,120
I'll show you how this game
should be done.

153
00:13:12,246 --> 00:13:14,957
Taste this one hundred-
eighty degree slap.

154
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:22,297
What did you do to me?

155
00:13:22,298 --> 00:13:23,591
Oh my god!

156
00:13:24,633 --> 00:13:25,759
I heard you're a queen here?

157
00:13:25,760 --> 00:13:28,846
Funny cause I can
only hear a whimpering dog.

158
00:13:29,680 --> 00:13:31,640
A pathetic bitch.

159
00:13:32,740 --> 00:13:34,158
You're going to regret this.

160
00:13:34,336 --> 00:13:35,961
Raze will know about this.

161
00:13:35,986 --> 00:13:37,446
Wow, go ahead.

162
00:13:37,471 --> 00:13:38,639
That's what you're good at.

163
00:13:39,108 --> 00:13:40,108
Coward.

164
00:13:45,362 --> 00:13:47,990
You'll regret this you
fucking bitch!

165
00:13:48,282 --> 00:13:50,117
I'll fucking kill you!

166
00:14:31,447 --> 00:14:32,447
Enter.

167
00:14:37,117 --> 00:14:38,118
Madam Violet.

168
00:14:38,287 --> 00:14:40,080
Supremo asked me to
give this to you.

169
00:14:44,517 --> 00:14:47,270
The council activities are
done for the day as well.

170
00:15:03,190 --> 00:15:05,693
Did something catch
your attention, Ms. Shion?

171
00:15:07,882 --> 00:15:08,882
It's nothing.

172
00:15:10,656 --> 00:15:12,449
You know curiousity

173
00:15:12,908 --> 00:15:15,077
is an important trait
that students should have.

174
00:15:22,042 --> 00:15:24,336
Did this pique your interest?

175
00:15:32,052 --> 00:15:34,180
I wasn't so ambitious before.

176
00:15:34,805 --> 00:15:37,224
I was content with teaching.

177
00:15:38,601 --> 00:15:39,727
But I see it clearly now.

178
00:15:40,686 --> 00:15:46,066
The systems people grow accustomed
to are not easily undone.

179
00:15:47,318 --> 00:15:49,028
So you build a new one.

180
00:15:53,324 --> 00:15:55,618
I attempted to climb the ranks

181
00:15:56,903 --> 00:15:58,988
to attain a position where I can

182
00:15:59,150 --> 00:16:02,853
dictate what I want
to happen to this school.

183
00:16:05,932 --> 00:16:07,976
I did okay. Didn't I, Ms. Shion?

184
00:16:09,347 --> 00:16:10,556
What do you think?

185
00:16:14,180 --> 00:16:15,598
Of course you do.

186
00:16:20,437 --> 00:16:22,814
I believe that I've
reminisced enough.

187
00:16:25,199 --> 00:16:27,659
You should go before
the Bloody Night starts.

188
00:16:28,442 --> 00:16:30,193
It's going to be such a shame

189
00:16:30,194 --> 00:16:31,612
if something happens...

190
00:16:32,021 --> 00:16:35,483
if the new SSG
Secretary disappears.

191
00:16:38,553 --> 00:16:39,763
So...

192
00:16:42,915 --> 00:16:44,374
I'm going to have someone else

193
00:16:44,375 --> 00:16:48,003
send these copies to the
SSG office tomorrow morning.

194
00:16:57,846 --> 00:16:59,556
You remind me of someone.

195
00:17:01,934 --> 00:17:02,934
Madam?

196
00:17:16,115 --> 00:17:17,616
You may go now, Ms. Shion.

197
00:17:46,103 --> 00:17:47,228
Come here.

198
00:17:47,229 --> 00:17:48,397
Vanessa, what's wrong?

199
00:17:48,422 --> 00:17:49,423
Is it true?

200
00:17:49,981 --> 00:17:51,691
You started a fight with Roxane?

201
00:17:53,777 --> 00:17:56,196
This place is a gossip
mill, isn't it?

202
00:17:57,656 --> 00:18:00,159
She had it coming, trust me.

203
00:18:00,242 --> 00:18:02,702
She was such a bitch, Van.

204
00:18:02,703 --> 00:18:03,287
If you only heard-

205
00:18:03,288 --> 00:18:04,913
That's not the point, Zein.

206
00:18:06,874 --> 00:18:08,083
Of course, it is.

207
00:18:09,001 --> 00:18:10,835
When did we ever let these

208
00:18:10,836 --> 00:18:13,547
bullies and bitches
get the better of us?

209
00:18:14,131 --> 00:18:15,674
That's when we were still outside,

210
00:18:16,759 --> 00:18:19,053
not here inside Hell U.

211
00:18:19,386 --> 00:18:20,929
You know how different it is here.

212
00:18:21,778 --> 00:18:23,112
Aren't you scared?

213
00:18:24,135 --> 00:18:26,053
You’re putting
yourself in danger.

214
00:18:26,521 --> 00:18:27,981
What do you want me to do?

215
00:18:28,536 --> 00:18:31,080
Let her push me around?

216
00:18:31,314 --> 00:18:32,314
Yes!

217
00:18:32,602 --> 00:18:35,104
Because you're not the only
one who'll be in danger.

218
00:18:35,652 --> 00:18:37,092
Didn't that cross that
head of yours?

219
00:18:38,697 --> 00:18:40,824
Instead of starting fights

220
00:18:41,450 --> 00:18:43,494
you should have focused on
climbing up the ranks.

221
00:18:43,922 --> 00:18:45,965
That should be our top priority!

222
00:18:52,449 --> 00:18:54,451
You only think about
yourself, don't you?

223
00:18:55,089 --> 00:18:57,299
Stop being selfish.

224
00:18:58,050 --> 00:19:01,136
Think of the rest of us for once.

225
00:19:14,942 --> 00:19:15,942
Hey!

226
00:19:16,318 --> 00:19:17,736
Are you done with our assignment?

227
00:19:18,737 --> 00:19:20,155
It's hard, isn't it?

228
00:19:20,447 --> 00:19:22,407
I can't find the answer
to question number three.

229
00:19:22,574 --> 00:19:23,658
Me too.

230
00:19:23,659 --> 00:19:25,327
I haven't answered everything yet.

231
00:19:25,536 --> 00:19:26,578
How about you guys?

232
00:19:26,912 --> 00:19:29,164
I'm not done yet.

233
00:19:30,290 --> 00:19:32,000
Let me copy your answers, Matt.

234
00:19:32,876 --> 00:19:33,752
Come on!

235
00:19:33,753 --> 00:19:36,754
Isn't our plan to study hard
so we can join Hell U's top ten?

236
00:19:36,755 --> 00:19:39,257
How is that going to happen
if you keep copying my work?

237
00:19:39,258 --> 00:19:41,050
Come on. Let me copy it!

238
00:19:41,051 --> 00:19:42,553
So we can finish it together.

239
00:19:42,845 --> 00:19:44,096
Please.

240
00:19:44,221 --> 00:19:45,346
Try to study.

241
00:19:45,347 --> 00:19:46,472
Are you sure that's the correct answer?

242
00:19:46,473 --> 00:19:48,100
You're complaining? Are you serious?

243
00:19:51,562 --> 00:19:52,563
Zein...

244
00:19:52,855 --> 00:19:53,855
your best friend is here.

245
00:19:56,692 --> 00:19:57,609
Why is she here?

246
00:19:57,610 --> 00:19:59,403
Supremo is asking for you.

247
00:20:02,239 --> 00:20:03,323
What does he want?

248
00:20:03,949 --> 00:20:05,325
I don't know!

249
00:20:05,784 --> 00:20:07,161
I'm just a messenger.

250
00:20:07,494 --> 00:20:10,663
All I know is he's waiting for you
at the SSG Office.

251
00:20:10,664 --> 00:20:13,583
Maybe this time you can do your job right.

252
00:20:13,584 --> 00:20:16,795
You keep hanging out with your friends.

253
00:20:19,965 --> 00:20:21,257
I'm sorry, guys.

254
00:20:21,258 --> 00:20:22,801
Supremo asked for me.

255
00:20:23,051 --> 00:20:25,846
Go ahead. It’s your responsibility.

256
00:20:26,388 --> 00:20:27,931
Don’t worry, we understand.

257
00:20:30,309 --> 00:20:31,934
Zein might get in trouble again.

258
00:20:31,935 --> 00:20:33,395
Zein is so stubborn.

259
00:21:10,098 --> 00:21:10,807
Hey!

260
00:21:10,807 --> 00:21:11,807
Oh shit...

261
00:21:13,018 --> 00:21:14,186
Stop that.

262
00:21:15,812 --> 00:21:17,439
Are you okay, Zein?

263
00:21:17,488 --> 00:21:19,615
Yes, better now.

264
00:21:20,526 --> 00:21:22,109
Are you and Van okay?

265
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:23,695
Did something happen?

266
00:21:25,364 --> 00:21:26,489
We had a fight.

267
00:21:26,490 --> 00:21:28,283
I need to apologize to her.

268
00:21:30,202 --> 00:21:33,830
Zein, I can see that you have
a lot of love for your friends.

269
00:21:34,289 --> 00:21:36,458
Of course, I do.

270
00:21:40,003 --> 00:21:41,463
But...

271
00:21:42,297 --> 00:21:44,466
I've noticed that your love has shifted.

272
00:21:44,883 --> 00:21:46,677
That Supremo

273
00:21:46,927 --> 00:21:49,596
you two are getting too close.

274
00:21:53,642 --> 00:21:55,394
Am I getting replaced?

275
00:21:56,895 --> 00:21:57,771
You know...

276
00:21:57,772 --> 00:21:58,980
we just seem close

277
00:21:58,981 --> 00:22:01,066
because we're always working together.

278
00:22:01,191 --> 00:22:04,027
What are you talking about, Matt?

279
00:22:06,572 --> 00:22:08,949
He doesn't even greet me good morning

280
00:22:09,157 --> 00:22:11,451
or ask about how my day was.

281
00:22:14,204 --> 00:22:15,872
For whatever reason

282
00:22:16,540 --> 00:22:17,708
he's isolated.

283
00:22:17,874 --> 00:22:19,543
Why do you seem disappointed?

284
00:22:21,587 --> 00:22:23,879
I'm joking.

285
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:26,550
I'm assured that I'm the one in your heart.

286
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:28,260
You're so lame.

287
00:22:28,635 --> 00:22:29,970
Lame?

288
00:22:30,178 --> 00:22:31,679
That's not lame, Zein.

289
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:33,515
I'm just telling the truth.

290
00:22:34,725 --> 00:22:36,685
I know I'm your crush.

291
00:22:39,855 --> 00:22:41,188
You know...

292
00:22:41,189 --> 00:22:42,523
that Supremo

293
00:22:42,524 --> 00:22:44,483
he's overworking you.

294
00:22:44,484 --> 00:22:47,112
I don't understand why
he keeps calling you.

295
00:22:50,574 --> 00:22:52,034
I just miss you.

296
00:22:52,826 --> 00:22:56,038
I miss having quality
time with my best friend.

297
00:22:58,957 --> 00:23:00,416
You know...

298
00:23:00,417 --> 00:23:01,668
I have to go in.

299
00:23:02,336 --> 00:23:04,211
Thank you for coming with me

300
00:23:04,212 --> 00:23:06,673
best friend.

301
00:23:07,674 --> 00:23:08,884
I'll head in.

302
00:23:09,509 --> 00:23:10,509
Okay.

303
00:23:10,594 --> 00:23:12,387
Wait, Zein.

304
00:23:12,846 --> 00:23:14,973
I have to ask you something.

305
00:23:15,682 --> 00:23:16,682
What is it?

306
00:23:16,767 --> 00:23:17,893
Who's more handsome

307
00:23:18,393 --> 00:23:20,604
me or that Supremo?

308
00:23:21,438 --> 00:23:24,900
Of course, you!

309
00:23:32,199 --> 00:23:33,230
You're late.

310
00:23:34,034 --> 00:23:35,369
Get inside.

311
00:23:49,424 --> 00:23:51,218
Bye.

312
00:24:09,027 --> 00:24:11,196
I have kept my side of the bargain

313
00:24:12,614 --> 00:24:13,739
haven't I?

314
00:24:13,740 --> 00:24:15,033
Ms. Shion?

315
00:24:16,827 --> 00:24:18,784
You have time for your friend

316
00:24:20,122 --> 00:24:21,748
but when I call upon you

317
00:24:23,667 --> 00:24:25,752
it's not right to keep me waiting.

318
00:24:26,378 --> 00:24:27,546
Am I right?

319
00:24:31,925 --> 00:24:33,468
You already know.

320
00:24:36,471 --> 00:24:37,806
Don’t be late again.

321
00:24:41,435 --> 00:24:43,520
But that's not your only fault

322
00:24:46,022 --> 00:24:47,524
you've been busy...

323
00:24:49,192 --> 00:24:50,569
reckless

324
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:53,029
a liability.

325
00:24:53,989 --> 00:24:55,741
The fight you started

326
00:24:58,067 --> 00:24:59,527
what did you gain?

327
00:25:03,373 --> 00:25:06,376
I slapped her 180 degrees

328
00:25:06,793 --> 00:25:09,254
it made me feel a whole lot better.

329
00:25:14,801 --> 00:25:17,429
Roxane is the queen of HU for fuck's sake.

330
00:25:19,306 --> 00:25:20,891
You're not allowed to touch her.

331
00:25:22,017 --> 00:25:23,518
What was your intention?

332
00:25:24,019 --> 00:25:26,262
You're nothing but a powerless secretary.

333
00:25:27,314 --> 00:25:28,607
Hell yes

334
00:25:29,065 --> 00:25:31,215
and I don't fucking care.

335
00:25:32,110 --> 00:25:34,279
If I get mistreated or hurt

336
00:25:34,821 --> 00:25:35,822
I'll fight back

337
00:25:37,074 --> 00:25:40,619
even if it's a queen or a supremo.

338
00:25:53,423 --> 00:25:54,508
Okay

339
00:25:55,008 --> 00:25:59,971
clearly my words aren't being
absorbed by that brain of yours.

340
00:26:00,472 --> 00:26:02,056
I'll level with you

341
00:26:02,057 --> 00:26:04,392
I'll speak in a language
you would understand

342
00:26:05,435 --> 00:26:07,369
clean the whole cafeteria.

343
00:26:08,522 --> 00:26:10,148
Excuse me?

344
00:26:10,364 --> 00:26:12,572
The whole cafeteria.

345
00:26:14,110 --> 00:26:15,946
Clean it for a week.

346
00:26:17,322 --> 00:26:18,740
Make it spotless

347
00:26:20,158 --> 00:26:21,158
shiny.

348
00:26:23,119 --> 00:26:24,287
Do you understand?

349
00:26:24,996 --> 00:26:26,164
For a week?

350
00:26:27,040 --> 00:26:28,040
For real?

351
00:26:29,209 --> 00:26:30,710
You can start today.

352
00:26:34,589 --> 00:26:36,383
Okay, fine.

353
00:26:36,758 --> 00:26:38,969
If that's all, goodbye...

354
00:26:39,761 --> 00:26:41,513
Supremo.

355
00:26:53,859 --> 00:26:56,820
Now, can anyone tell me

356
00:26:57,153 --> 00:26:59,906
why hope is a core human value?

357
00:27:01,199 --> 00:27:04,536
It's different compared to
what we previously discussed.

358
00:27:05,912 --> 00:27:07,548
Come on, class.

359
00:27:09,124 --> 00:27:11,042
This is important.

360
00:27:12,377 --> 00:27:13,628
Anyone?

361
00:27:14,588 --> 00:27:15,714
Hope

362
00:27:16,214 --> 00:27:18,425
is not a wish or a dream

363
00:27:18,675 --> 00:27:20,260
it’s faith.

364
00:27:20,969 --> 00:27:25,055
Faith that what we wish for will come true.

365
00:27:25,056 --> 00:27:26,765
Like our faith

366
00:27:26,766 --> 00:27:28,726
that we will enter heaven

367
00:27:28,727 --> 00:27:30,395
when we pass on.

368
00:27:30,812 --> 00:27:32,105
At least

369
00:27:32,689 --> 00:27:34,441
that’s what i think.

370
00:27:34,983 --> 00:27:37,109
Very good, Lyka.

371
00:27:37,110 --> 00:27:39,987
Hope is the sister of faith.

372
00:27:39,988 --> 00:27:41,196
And together

373
00:27:41,197 --> 00:27:42,907
they allow us to believe

374
00:27:42,908 --> 00:27:44,492
in a better future.

375
00:27:52,857 --> 00:27:55,669
Is Lyka Ms. Aya's favorite student?

376
00:27:56,588 --> 00:27:59,090
They seem to glow when they're talking.

377
00:27:59,883 --> 00:28:01,301
Is she her mentor?

378
00:28:02,385 --> 00:28:05,680
Ahh... they look like family.

379
00:28:06,431 --> 00:28:07,682
Whatever their relationship is.

380
00:28:08,058 --> 00:28:10,852
It's nice to see moments
like this in Hell U

381
00:28:12,854 --> 00:28:14,105
laughter

382
00:28:14,439 --> 00:28:16,274
protecting each other

383
00:28:16,900 --> 00:28:18,860
like me and my friends.

384
00:28:19,861 --> 00:28:24,240
They are the reason I survive in this hell.

385
00:28:25,617 --> 00:28:27,744
I really need to apologize to Van.

386
00:28:35,835 --> 00:28:37,170
Celine.

387
00:28:37,879 --> 00:28:39,506
Are you okay?

388
00:28:40,090 --> 00:28:41,277
You look...

389
00:28:42,092 --> 00:28:43,761
They're coming

390
00:28:44,302 --> 00:28:46,066
be careful, Zein.

391
00:28:52,310 --> 00:28:54,229
This isn't a joke, Zein.

392
00:28:54,646 --> 00:28:56,606
You're in danger.

393
00:28:58,149 --> 00:28:59,149
All of us.

394
00:29:00,902 --> 00:29:03,071
There's a traitor among your friends

395
00:29:03,905 --> 00:29:06,866
they're about to know
what's missing in the formula.

396
00:29:08,451 --> 00:29:09,953
If I were you

397
00:29:10,370 --> 00:29:12,872
I'll strike first.

398
00:29:35,270 --> 00:29:37,105
Thanks a lot, Supremo.

399
00:29:37,272 --> 00:29:38,731
You asshole.

400
00:29:38,732 --> 00:29:41,150
Way important things are happening

401
00:29:41,151 --> 00:29:43,778
and I'm wasting my time
cleaning this shithole.

402
00:29:45,530 --> 00:29:46,740
He's already heartless,

403
00:29:46,906 --> 00:29:49,346
how can be still be so oblivious
to other people's struggles?

404
00:29:52,203 --> 00:29:54,372
No, oblivious isn't the right word for him.

405
00:29:54,706 --> 00:29:57,375
It's too generous.

406
00:29:58,168 --> 00:30:00,503
He decided this punishment
knowing the circumstances.

407
00:30:00,837 --> 00:30:03,840
He's just being a dick.

408
00:31:03,566 --> 00:31:05,110
You missed a spot.

409
00:31:06,277 --> 00:31:07,987
Don't forget to sweep the crevices.

410
00:31:09,155 --> 00:31:10,990
Yes, boss.

411
00:31:16,788 --> 00:31:19,039
Do you have a family?

412
00:31:19,040 --> 00:31:20,558
Ms. Shion?

413
00:31:21,709 --> 00:31:22,794
Huh?

414
00:31:23,545 --> 00:31:24,545
Family.

415
00:31:27,215 --> 00:31:29,551
Why are you suddenly
engaging in small talk?

416
00:31:30,844 --> 00:31:31,845
Are you bored?

417
00:31:33,138 --> 00:31:34,514
You never know

418
00:31:35,098 --> 00:31:38,726
maybe if we talk a bit you'll clean faster.

419
00:31:39,561 --> 00:31:41,771
So we can leave the cafeteria.

420
00:31:41,772 --> 00:31:47,789
(Watch on www.dramacool.club Support Admin)

421
00:31:42,814 --> 00:31:43,814
So

422
00:31:44,649 --> 00:31:45,733
Indulge me.

423
00:31:46,985 --> 00:31:48,319
I'm going to ask again.

424
00:31:48,987 --> 00:31:50,752
How's your family, Ms. Shion?

425
00:32:04,669 --> 00:32:05,670
I guess.

426
00:32:07,130 --> 00:32:09,799
We're a normal family.

427
00:32:11,426 --> 00:32:12,719
My mom

428
00:32:17,265 --> 00:32:18,266
is hardworking

429
00:32:18,766 --> 00:32:20,268
affectionate

430
00:32:20,810 --> 00:32:22,770
and is addicted to watching shows.

431
00:32:23,980 --> 00:32:25,940
My older sister Allison.

432
00:32:27,817 --> 00:32:29,527
Textbook eldest daughter

433
00:32:31,446 --> 00:32:33,448
she's good at everything, she's beautiful

434
00:32:34,199 --> 00:32:35,259
and brave.

435
00:32:37,058 --> 00:32:39,477
My mom's stressed all the time because

436
00:32:40,455 --> 00:32:42,649
her two daughters are fighters.

437
00:32:44,584 --> 00:32:45,792
There was one time

438
00:32:45,793 --> 00:32:47,479
when we ate at an
unlimited samgyupsal place.

439
00:32:47,503 --> 00:32:50,924
Someone flirted with Allison

440
00:32:53,968 --> 00:32:55,261
and...

441
00:32:55,595 --> 00:32:57,363
Again, we're a normal family.

442
00:32:58,848 --> 00:33:00,230
I miss them.

443
00:33:01,809 --> 00:33:03,311
I see.

444
00:33:04,062 --> 00:33:05,688
How about your friends?

445
00:33:06,231 --> 00:33:07,982
How are they?

446
00:33:08,566 --> 00:33:10,443
You already know them, don't you?

447
00:33:11,694 --> 00:33:12,737
Yeah, but

448
00:33:12,987 --> 00:33:14,239
by name only.

449
00:33:14,739 --> 00:33:17,784
My duties don't really get
me to meet the students.

450
00:33:18,243 --> 00:33:19,917
Only if they crossed the line.

451
00:33:24,666 --> 00:33:26,152
My friends.

452
00:33:28,503 --> 00:33:30,191
We're like family too.

453
00:33:31,339 --> 00:33:33,675
Mia is the heart of the group

454
00:33:34,259 --> 00:33:36,177
she's like sushine.

455
00:33:36,928 --> 00:33:38,680
Dave and Jerome

456
00:33:39,639 --> 00:33:41,933
they're trouble in the best way.

457
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:44,143
If you need to laugh

458
00:33:44,352 --> 00:33:45,645
they're the best ones to go to.

459
00:33:49,607 --> 00:33:51,526
Vanessa...

460
00:33:54,988 --> 00:33:59,117
matter of fact, Van is braver than me.

461
00:33:59,867 --> 00:34:02,954
If she thinks something will hurt us

462
00:34:05,748 --> 00:34:08,710
she'll call it out without
hurting us even if she's mad.

463
00:34:13,172 --> 00:34:14,552
Matt...

464
00:34:17,135 --> 00:34:18,599
he's my constant.

465
00:34:22,015 --> 00:34:23,807
How about you, Supremo?

466
00:34:23,808 --> 00:34:26,519
I shouldn't be the only one sharing things.

467
00:34:27,194 --> 00:34:28,825
What's your family like?

468
00:34:29,522 --> 00:34:30,522
Friends?

469
00:34:34,235 --> 00:34:36,279
Chaotic.

470
00:34:38,171 --> 00:34:40,099
It's a long story, Ms. Shion.

471
00:34:41,784 --> 00:34:43,328
I'll tell you next time.

472
00:34:45,330 --> 00:34:46,914
- Don't forget to sweep the.
- Crevices.

473
00:34:47,206 --> 00:34:48,583
I know.

474
00:34:49,625 --> 00:34:50,918
I know.

475
00:35:36,988 --> 00:35:37,739
I'm done.

476
00:35:37,882 --> 00:35:39,092
Can I go?

477
00:35:40,426 --> 00:35:42,095
A bit slower than I thought.

478
00:35:47,266 --> 00:35:48,266
But

479
00:35:48,935 --> 00:35:50,228
you're good to go.

480
00:36:15,378 --> 00:36:17,255
I'll go ahead, Supremo.

481
00:36:18,339 --> 00:36:19,339
Okay.

482
00:37:49,597 --> 00:37:50,890
Go faster!

483
00:37:52,767 --> 00:37:53,870
Stay quiet!

484
00:38:15,164 --> 00:38:17,625
No one has ever
attempted to hurt the queen.

485
00:38:19,377 --> 00:38:21,212
I'm actually impressed.

486
00:38:21,587 --> 00:38:24,048
What do you think the boss will do to her?

487
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:27,969
Death. I'm sure he'll kill her.

488
00:38:31,806 --> 00:38:34,475
This one's a fighter.

489
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:35,643
Let her be.

490
00:38:36,102 --> 00:38:39,020
Let's just see where
her bravery will get her

491
00:38:39,021 --> 00:38:40,565
once the boss arrives.

492
00:38:47,863 --> 00:38:48,863
Is that her?

493
00:38:49,240 --> 00:38:50,240
Yes, boss.

494
00:38:51,409 --> 00:38:52,577
Leave us.

495
00:39:17,689 --> 00:39:20,484
An eye for an eye for Roxane.

496
00:39:22,690 --> 00:39:25,610
Nice to meet you, Zein.

497
00:39:26,527 --> 00:39:29,405
I am Raze Silvenia.

498
00:39:32,066 --> 00:39:33,401
You sure are brave

499
00:39:34,327 --> 00:39:36,120
like what they said.

500
00:39:40,541 --> 00:39:42,501
But how about your friends?

501
00:39:43,379 --> 00:39:45,415
Are they as brave as you?

502
00:39:50,718 --> 00:39:54,013
Maybe I'll punish them instead?

503
00:39:54,847 --> 00:39:57,808
I can start with Mia.

504
00:39:59,143 --> 00:40:02,730
I bet she shrieks when she gets hurt.

505
00:40:04,774 --> 00:40:07,360
My patience is running thin.

506
00:40:08,235 --> 00:40:10,403
I carry death with me.

507
00:40:10,404 --> 00:40:12,365
And believe me

508
00:40:12,782 --> 00:40:15,993
he'll come for you, Zein Shion.

509
00:40:27,838 --> 00:40:29,790
Raze Silvenia?

510
00:40:34,512 --> 00:40:36,586
Maybe you'd like to release me

511
00:40:37,139 --> 00:40:40,184
before I reveal your secret to everyone.

512
00:40:41,894 --> 00:40:44,230
I don't know any secrets of mine

513
00:40:44,438 --> 00:40:46,857
that you can use against me.

514
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:52,613
You can't faze me, Zein Shion.

515
00:40:53,656 --> 00:40:55,282
Is that so?

516
00:40:56,492 --> 00:40:59,787
You’re sure that you don’t have a secret

517
00:41:00,162 --> 00:41:01,956
that can kill you

518
00:41:02,289 --> 00:41:04,333
when it’s revealed?

519
00:41:05,710 --> 00:41:08,087
What secret of mine do you know?

520
00:41:10,840 --> 00:41:14,301
Just because you wear his mask

521
00:41:15,136 --> 00:41:18,431
doesn't mean you can fool everyone.

522
00:41:19,473 --> 00:41:22,017
You're not Raze Silvenia.

523
00:41:28,816 --> 00:41:29,816
See?

524
00:41:30,609 --> 00:41:32,903
One mention of his name

525
00:41:33,446 --> 00:41:35,364
you're already fazed.

526
00:41:36,574 --> 00:41:40,536
No one can compare to how terrifying he is.

527
00:41:41,746 --> 00:41:44,749
It doesn't matter how many masks you wear

528
00:41:45,499 --> 00:41:48,048
you can't fool me when it comes to Raze.

529
00:41:51,964 --> 00:41:54,467
I've already met the real Raze.

530
00:42:07,271 --> 00:42:09,236
Even if it's just one time.

531
00:42:10,691 --> 00:42:12,759
I can see the differences.

532
00:42:14,487 --> 00:42:18,032
You can't compare to Raze.

533
00:42:18,616 --> 00:42:20,075
You?

534
00:42:21,285 --> 00:42:22,410
You're lucky

535
00:42:22,411 --> 00:42:24,496
if I can remember you tomorrow.

536
00:42:24,497 --> 00:42:25,747
Shut your mouth!

537
00:42:25,748 --> 00:42:26,873
Boss?

538
00:42:26,874 --> 00:42:27,792
What happened?

539
00:42:27,793 --> 00:42:29,460
We heard a scream.

540
00:42:29,794 --> 00:42:30,878
I'm okay.

541
00:42:31,462 --> 00:42:32,588
Get out!

542
00:42:42,473 --> 00:42:43,849
If I'm being honest.

543
00:42:44,266 --> 00:42:46,477
I can kill you now.

544
00:42:47,812 --> 00:42:50,272
But they won't allow it.

545
00:42:55,194 --> 00:42:56,194
I'm impressed.

546
00:42:57,029 --> 00:42:58,614
I underestimated you, Zein.

547
00:43:01,867 --> 00:43:03,408
I fooled everyone!

548
00:43:05,204 --> 00:43:07,122
I even fooled Roxane.

549
00:43:14,755 --> 00:43:17,299
This complicates things.

550
00:43:18,425 --> 00:43:22,179
Maybe we can help each other?

551
00:43:23,514 --> 00:43:24,514
Oh?

552
00:43:25,057 --> 00:43:27,268
Now you have authority?

553
00:43:28,018 --> 00:43:30,670
Enough to make you an offer.

554
00:43:33,023 --> 00:43:35,014
6:53 pm.

555
00:43:37,820 --> 00:43:39,113
I'll set you free

556
00:43:39,795 --> 00:43:41,297
but you can't betray me.

557
00:43:42,032 --> 00:43:45,160
Wow, the sudden kindness irks me.

558
00:43:48,455 --> 00:43:50,207
The clock's ticking.

559
00:43:51,792 --> 00:43:53,544
Do you want to leave

560
00:43:54,211 --> 00:43:58,215
and keep this secret between us.

561
00:44:01,218 --> 00:44:02,970
What's your answer, Zein?

562
00:44:03,846 --> 00:44:05,306
Deal.

563
00:45:13,832 --> 00:45:17,628
Your secret is my secret.

564
00:45:29,598 --> 00:45:30,683
Zein

565
00:45:32,768 --> 00:45:34,812
stop finding him.

566
00:47:25,047 --> 00:47:26,381
Let go of me!

567
00:47:41,688 --> 00:47:42,688
Come here!

568
00:47:43,065 --> 00:47:43,857
You can't escape from me.

569
00:47:43,857 --> 00:47:44,566
Let go of me!

570
00:47:44,567 --> 00:47:45,983
You thought you could escape?

571
00:47:45,984 --> 00:47:47,528
I said let go!

572
00:47:55,494 --> 00:47:56,774
Where do you think you're going?

573
00:47:57,788 --> 00:47:58,872
Get away!

574
00:48:02,251 --> 00:48:03,335
I said get away from me!

575
00:48:08,590 --> 00:48:09,590
Ms. Shion.

576
00:48:09,925 --> 00:48:13,387
But I don't have any idea
where the hidden laboratory is.

577
00:48:13,846 --> 00:48:16,890
Just do your job as a secretary

578
00:48:18,308 --> 00:48:21,103
and monitor all their movements.

579
00:48:22,396 --> 00:48:24,231
What if they find out I'm the mole?

580
00:48:29,361 --> 00:48:31,446
I'm not ready to die yet, Sir Alvarez.

581
00:48:33,907 --> 00:48:35,159
I still need to escape

582
00:48:36,285 --> 00:48:37,744
with my friends.

583
00:48:38,328 --> 00:48:39,788
Please help us!

584
00:48:40,164 --> 00:48:44,501
We thought you're the next
Samantha but you're both useless!

585
00:48:45,127 --> 00:48:46,128
I thought

586
00:48:47,379 --> 00:48:48,922
you're like Samantha

587
00:48:50,174 --> 00:48:51,174
but I was wrong.

588
00:48:51,717 --> 00:48:53,302
I'm just a secretary.

589
00:48:53,927 --> 00:48:55,637
Stay away from Alvarez.

590
00:48:57,598 --> 00:48:58,640
Why do you care?

591
00:48:59,099 --> 00:49:01,101
Good morning, our dear students.

592
00:49:01,810 --> 00:49:03,478
We are gathered here today

593
00:49:03,896 --> 00:49:06,940
to honor our late headmaster

594
00:49:07,149 --> 00:49:08,692
Dominic Valdez.

595
00:49:08,942 --> 00:49:11,403
You killed the late headmaster!

596
00:49:11,862 --> 00:49:13,405
You both should be punished!

597
00:49:14,198 --> 00:49:15,198
Get rid of her.

598
00:49:15,449 --> 00:49:16,241
Stop!

599
00:49:16,408 --> 00:49:17,408
Let go of me!

600
00:49:17,659 --> 00:49:19,036
Don't cross the admin.

601
00:49:20,037 --> 00:49:21,037
Or me.

602
00:49:24,541 --> 00:49:25,541
Hey...

603
00:49:26,293 --> 00:49:27,544
what's bothering you?

604
00:49:28,170 --> 00:49:29,171
Let me help you.
